<p><ent>Manx cat</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Manx
<hw>Manx</hw>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>The language of the inhabitants
of the Isle of Man, a dialect of the Celtic.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Many</ent>⟦br⟧
